Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander to all units:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu will hold them back with Inori's Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During that time, we'll seize the second truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The target will be at the attack point in six,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,five,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,four,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,three,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,two,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the holdup?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, make it quick! They'll spot us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! They've spotted us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu, what's wrong?! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, everyone will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.94,0:00:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander to all units, abort mission! Abort mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:44.41,Copy of OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur2}Blooming wildflower
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you love me, Shu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:52.81,Copy of OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur2}I beg you, please tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then promise me something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\i1}Promise you'll make your big sister happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:03:02.87,Copy of OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur2}Summer's sun clouded over, the wind streamed by
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:10.78,Copy of OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur2}The two overlapped
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake? I'm coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Shu! Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast. It's a sandwich, is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you surprised me yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you messaged me out of nowhere asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to tell me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you want to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can tell me when you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let him be for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, hasn't it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Tsutsugami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my comrades call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a surprise. I certainly never thought you were {\i1}his{\i0} son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"His"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I have to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutsugami Gai, why do you fight? What is it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one special woman out there that I want to hold in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saving Japan is a side project to getting your woman, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rock we discussed will be brought to Haneda the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Yan is trying to transport it overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that should remain in the grasp of the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We'll use all our strength to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought this rock, the object of every nation's desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would fall into my hands like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will take you another step closer to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an ambitious woman, Emily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose the unknown is Keido.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He steals this, and then instead of running he waltzes right back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you feel like coming back to school, Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's really not good for you to hole up in that place forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori's... out today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu, so you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where've you been, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, sure, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get you some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done. I want to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're ready to give up on everything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just because you couldn't save one kid with the cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed. So I thought I could be like Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just Ouma Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're wallowing in self-pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up already, Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait. Give me just a little more—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know where the stolen rock that started it all is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running a recovery mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got nothing to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never wanted this stupid power in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}sick{\i0} of it, do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it's possible to isolate the Void Genome if its possessor dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to test that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a dead man now. Don't show your face in front of us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have Inori pull out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was stupid to think for even a second that you were one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, calls or texts or something... can we...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a new song. I'd like you to listen to it, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm just sort of—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I must've wanted to be like Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it was impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. Everything's gone back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It should be better this way, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too salty, Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major General Yan will be temporarily returning home on that craft with some top-secret materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our duty is to see him safely off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this thing! Right, men?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Major General should be arriving any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daryl...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The cycle is getting short.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I... near my limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I... a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Shu tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fall in love with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Gai, do I love Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you chose him too, in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Survive first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll think about this afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by this, Chief Keido?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you use Kurosu's ID to steal that rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not to mention hand it over to Major General Yan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a familiar face on the island. He's grown a lot, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't involve Shu in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late for that. He's already inherited the King's Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu has... the Void Genome?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all. He's in with the Undertakers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuriha Inori. You've met her too, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe a girl with that face, that body,{ that ass,}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is by his side through mere coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Begin the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be at Point B in 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that point there are surveillance cameras and monitors
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I can't control from here, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander to all units:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have thirty minutes until our objective's transport plane takes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My team will seize the plane before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Endlave unit will deploy when we announce the seizure and back us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You summoned {\i1}me{\i0} out here too, so don't screw it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(658,611)}We've been expecting you, Major General Yan!{station message}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the transport plane ready?{station message}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir! Everything's been fully prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under Major Segai's careful command.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch the camera to channel G7.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such channel, Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, naturally. After all, I just now set it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we ready for broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All set, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be outputted from every channel in the city that's under GHQ control.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Major Segai. All my beloved members of the Anti Bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take Vaccine D now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat: All my beloved members of the Anti Bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take Vaccine D now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust this will do, Chief Keido?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come crying to me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Gai's team?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. They've boarded the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... it's too late to back out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unmanned?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutsugami Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending you to heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I'd gotten to hear the rest of the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the Classics a lot, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I say so all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?{this reminds me of that scene in Code Geass where Lelouch thinks of raping Kallen}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be close to you, Hare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all... you love me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hare!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Hare!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try telling me exactly what you did wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not seeing me at all, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me a substitute for Yuzuriha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your big new power make it so you can't even see yourself anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you draw something like scissors out of Yahiro and destroy an Endlave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt so bad for you then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wanted to help cheer you up somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that Shu just now wasn't okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the Shu I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Hare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, the controls don't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi, cut the remote controls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is genetic resonance!{what}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's activated the stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to fetch you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argo! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you possibly be thinking of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humanity's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finish what we started on that day... on that Christmas we lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's this bad feeling?{getting rejected by Hare}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the right song!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll... wake up...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Shuichiro, you're old enough to know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as entertaining as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
